          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "25 marks - Identification of challenge (with examples)",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "There was very effective identification of the challenges, the discussion was clearly authentic and",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "text" : " ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "text" : "demonstrated very good depth of thought, and very specific evidence to supporting evidence was",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "text" : " ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "text" : "included and explained effectively.",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "25 marks - Attendance and documentation (the video of u attending the workshop)",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "The student attended at least 3 workshops and provided clear and engaging documentation of",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "text" : " ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "text" : "their attendance for all of them in the reflection.",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "25 marks - Reflection on improvement (how you think you’ve improved, with examples)",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "The discussion of workshop takeaways\/future applications is very clear and demonstrates",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "text" : " ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "text" : "excellent depth of thought.",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "25 marks - Creative effort in reflection (just don’t write an essay)",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "Very clear efforts were made to include a variety of media in a very engaging and creative way that",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "text" : " ",
                              "type" : "text"
                            },
                            {
                              "text" : "accented the ideas presented in the reflection very effectively.",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
